snippet.title: Trigger Rally 0.6.4 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Open source rally racing game Trigger Rally 0.6.4. Showing off some of the features and maps, all three cars and voices.
Get Trigger Rally from http://trigger-rally.sf.net

More Trigger videos in https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLz8BV_VUaS9RgHf09Pdg6zLPffI5g6GwN

We update regularly - subscribe to stay in the loop! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCaoiUeZllBKcQlNi5DREjYg?sub_confirmation=1
